{"tid":2045763,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］渡辺麻友從良引退！！！","createTime":"2020-06-01T04:06:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T04:55:32.000Z","uid":6940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c55c88de37a3a577697efc4641fbe721a320e090","tid":2045763,"uid":6940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T04:06:23.000Z","msg":"渡辺麻友 透過事務所正式發表從藝能界引退，主要原因是健康問題，未知實際情況如何，或許是身心也受到很大壓力而沒法承受，在這裡只有希望麻友早日康復，無論在那裡也得到幸福。<br />\n<br />\n麻友畢業後想走演藝路線，也曾拍過幾套主演劇集，但都因為劇本或演出問題而沒得到太好評價，始終演員與偶像是兩個不同世界，競爭非常大，像前田敦子或大島優子也需要花上很多年才能找到自己位置。"},{"pid":"f40c3ca41bdafdd46851f9481c498c2b8dcaf7dc","tid":2045763,"uid":53062,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T04:10:32.000Z","msg":"俾人搞大個肚"},{"pid":"d3d4968242138052d148e4dcce7eb1628e80e7f1","tid":2045763,"uid":19012,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T04:14:58.000Z","msg":"2020 剛剛好一半"},{"pid":"b4ce56b27e19ff6957caef7f5594236ec5ef8a13","tid":2045763,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T04:16:32.000Z","msg":"Fake news"},{"pid":"c4a51c3eb8b11fc559514087b34c787ce7953a05","tid":2045763,"uid":200465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T04:16:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69b844077991eaa9bd81d376446b840397f7a45a","tid":2045763,"uid":169618,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T04:20:28.000Z","msg":"從良? 佢搞咩嚟?"},{"pid":"ffa18b40520f7a46d31ef7fec14cf04ad04a8dd9","tid":2045763,"uid":7922,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T04:20:59.000Z","msg":"下海了<br />\n<br />\n希望快d下馬多p"},{"pid":"a3c5561ba5709cfe9a8ed4e316ce6d83243ce5ec","tid":2045763,"uid":200465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"69b844077991eaa9bd81d376446b840397f7a45a","tid":2045763,"uid":169618,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime"